dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning in Bayfield county in 2020. The following features are included: AIRPORT, GENERAL, and SHORELAND.”For SHORELAND: [This layer contains shoreland zoning data for Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata.] For GENERAL: [This layer contains zoning district data for Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata.] For AIRPORT: [This layer contains airport location data in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
